OL,4,C'exhausted' and 'isolated' over daily
OL,5,Cstruggles
OL,7,FExhausting, isolating and soul-
OL,8,Fdestroying: that is how parents of
OL,9,Fchildren with additional learning
OL,10,Fneeds describe the daily battle they
OL,11,Fface to try and ensure their families
OL,12,Fcan thrive.
OL,14,FFamilies have told ITV Cymru Wales
OL,15,Fthere are significant gaps in
OL,16,Feducation and childcare provision for
OL,17,Ftheir children, while a damning report
OL,18,Fon the sector in Wales has exposed
OL,19,Fmajor shortcomings.
