OL,7,FFor many, this is the everyday reality
OL,8,Fof fighting to try and ensure their
OL,9,Fchild has the best possible start to
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,FBetsan Gower Gallagher's seven-year-
OL,13,Fold twins Brielle and Bowann are both
OL,14,Fautistic.
OL,16,F"They're like fireworks," she said.
OL,17,F"They are full of joy and full of
OL,18,Fexcitement and sheer delight.
