OL,7,FIt deemed that access to school was
OL,8,Fnot consistently equal across Wales,
OL,9,Fwith examples of good practice patchy.
OL,10,FThe report said: "Too often, it is too
OL,11,Fdependent on individual staff or
OL,12,Ffamilies working hard. There is no way
OL,13,Fof making sure it happens across
OL,14,FWales."
OL,16,FSchools and local authorities not
OL,17,Fhaving enough money or staff and a
OL,18,Flack of understanding of certain
OL,19,Fconditions are among the reasons cited.
