OL,7,FThe committee also found there was not
OL,8,Fequal access to childcare at the
OL,9,Fmoment, with long-distance travel
OL,10,Foften required, and not enough being
OL,11,Fdone to fill the gaps in inclusive
OL,12,Fchildcare.
OL,14,FCommittee chair Buffy Williams MS told
OL,15,FITV Cymru Wales that two of the
OL,16,Fbiggest issues were funding and staff
OL,17,Ftraining.
