OL,7,F"It's almost like we're failing the
OL,8,Fmost vulnerable children in our
OL,9,Fsociety by not ensuring that they have
OL,10,Fan equal playing field where education
OL,11,Fis concerned," she said.
OL,13,F"It does feel like that we have a
OL,14,Fsignificant amount of children in
OL,15,FWales that are being failed and
OL,16,Fforgotten about.
OL,18,F"It is definitely a postcode lottery.
OL,19,FWe need to be doing more and we need
OL,20,Fto be doing better."
