OL,5,Cstruggles
OL,7,F"There are currently too many children
OL,8,Fand young people who are not in school
OL,9,Fcurrently because schools are not able
OL,10,Fto meet their needs. This is having a
OL,11,Flong-term effect on the child but also
OL,12,Fit's having a huge strain on parents.
OL,14,F"There is also currently a lack of
OL,15,Fresources in the Welsh language, and
OL,16,Fthere have been many cases highlighted
OL,17,Fto Plaid Cymru where the language of
OL,18,Fthe home has been changed to adapt to
OL,19,Fthe education of the child. This
OL,20,Fshould not have to be the case.
